Security Highlights:
Password Hashing: Uses PASSWORD_DEFAULT (bcrypt) for industry-standard encryption.

XSS Prevention: All user-rendered data is escaped using htmlspecialchars().

Session Fixation: New session IDs are generated upon successful login.

Prepared Statements: Prevents malicious SQL input.

